@@ -0,0 +1,37 @@
+# FIX Parser Calibration Experiments
+
+Six self-contained experiment programs for optimising the CT-DP FIX
+expression-template parser configuration.
+
+## Quick Start
+
+```bash
+# Build with mock measurement (no hardware required)
+cmake -B build -DCTDP_BUILD_EXPERIMENTS=ON -DEXPERIMENT_MOCK=ON -DCTDP_BUILD_TESTS=ON
+cmake --build build
+
+# Run unit tests
+ctest --test-dir build --output-on-failure -R test_extractors
+```
+
+## Programs
+
+| Program | Target | Encoding | Question |
+|---------|--------|----------|----------|
+| A | p50 | one-hot (36) | Does pipeline work on easy target? |
+| B | p99 | one-hot (36) | How much harder is p99? |
+| C | log(p99) | one-hot (36) | Does log transform help? |
+| D | log(p99) | + counts (40) | Do composition features help? |
+| E | log(p99) | + transitions (56) | Do adjacency features help? |
+| F | exhaustive | N/A | Ground truth (1,024 configs) |
+
+## Directory Structure
+
+```
+common/          Shared headers (extractors, config, measurement, output)
+programs/        The six experiment programs (A–F)
+generated/       Committed constexpr candidate headers (two-phase build)
+results/         JSON output (gitignored)
+tests/           Unit and integration tests
+scripts/         Batch automation
+```
